data.title: 12SEAGC1996 Deep Excavation Work Near MRT Structures, Chua Tong Seng
data.meta_description: 12SEAGC1996 Deep Excavation Work Near MRT Structures, Chua Tong Seng - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document summarizes a deep excavation project near a Singapore MRT station that required special consideration to minimize disturbance to the sensitive MRT structures. A unique semi-top-down construction method was used involving a diaphragm wall system as a temporary retaining wall and permanent building wall. Instrumentation monitored the excavation's effects, and analysis of the wall considered its interaction with soil and construction sequencing.
